commits.author: Robert Muir
commits.sourceNew:
/** * Get the bytes to be added to the category token payload for this * enhancement. *

* NOTE: The returned array is copied, it is recommended to allocate a * new one each time. *

* The bytes generated by this method are the input of * {@link #extractCategoryTokenData(byte[], int, int)}. * * @param categoryAttribute * The attribute of the category. * @return The bytes to be added to the category token payload for this * enhancement. */ byte[] getCategoryTokenBytes(CategoryAttribute categoryAttribute);
